value.0: After escape we split up. Yesgar say we harder to find that way. Now me see bounty hunter everywhere. Me kills all, but you is tough. You is great warrior.

value.0: Me see noble warrior spirit inside you too. Now, for us: we should fight. Me want to see if me can defeat you.
